    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 36-39.</p><p>Level 23</p><p>Heraldic Favor</p><p>Beginning at 23rd level, you become the foremost herald of your God. Your voice is theirs, and you can</p><p>perform miracles in their name. After successfully performing a Divine Intervention, you can do so again after you complete a long rest, instead of having to wait 7 days. In addition, your Divine Intervention becomes even more powerful, able to replicate any spell of 9th level or lower from the Cleric spell list.</p></div>",
